<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Hike down the steep, verdant volcanic crater rim to touch the crystal-clear waters.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Spot varied birdlife, monkeys, and unique flora in a peaceful, untouched sanctuary.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Relax or paddle along the quiet edges of a lake split between two countries.</li>
