    <ol style="padding-left:22px;margin-bottom:8px">
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">08:00 AM: Drive from Arusha or Moshi through vibrant rural towns towards the Kenyan border.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">10:00 AM: Arrive at Lake Chala and take a guided walk along the high crater rim to enjoy the panoramic views.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">11:00 AM: Carefully hike down the forest-lined path to the water&#39;s edge.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">12:30 PM: Enjoy a relaxing lunch by the water or at a designated lakeside viewpoint.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">01:30 PM: Spend time exploring the nature trails, birdwatching, or relaxing in the serene environment.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">03:30 PM: Hike back up to the crater rim and drive back to town.</li>
